snippet.title: MY LITTLE PONY: A Maretime Bay Adventure | Launch Trailer | Australia / New Zealand | ACB
snippet.description:
#MyLittlePony #AMaretimeBayAdventure is out now! Magic is back, but it's unbalanced. In fact, we're starting to see it run rampant across Maretime Bay and our heroes will have to work together to find out why. New magic, new adventures, iconic locations - if you're a My Little Pony fan, you can't miss it!

Learn and adventure with our brave and enchanting heroes and let them inspire you with their positive messages of kindness, friendship,... Get yours today and enjoy this epic adventure! 

https://outrightgames.com/au/games/my-little-pony-a-maretime-bay-adventure/
